{"about_the_game":"Collect your favorite tiles, manipulate your draws and discards, and aim for continuous wins and high scores!<br>Yes, like the endless sky that knows no bounds!<br><strong>Sky's The Limit MAH-JONG</strong> offers mechanisms that make the impossible possible, something you can't experience in regular Mahjong. How you use these mechanisms is up to you.<br>Whether you're pursuing the strongest hands, crafting beautiful hands with dedication, or relentlessly collecting Dora, in <strong>Sky's The Limit MAH-JONG</strong>, you can immerse yourself in your own Mahjong game without any interference.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tile Trading</h2>Collect your preferred tiles at the trading shop, build your deck, and devise strategies to counteract luck.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/Trade2.gif?t=1731113891\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Special Tiles</h2>Make effective use of special Dora and bonus tiles to gain an advantage in your games.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/SpPais.gif?t=1731113891\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">New Possibilities with Deck Building</h2><strong>&quot;There is no need for only four of the same tile in the deck.&quot; </strong>Your choices can create hands that are impossible in reality!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/Ton.gif?t=1731113891\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Boost Status</h2>Manipulate the number of draws and discards, and even control the Dora to create the best environment to strengthen your hands.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/Enchant.gif?t=1731113891\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">No-Ceiling Scoring System (Ao-Tenjo)</h2>Score calculation is based on the Ao-Tenjo rule, meaning points are not capped, and all the Fu and Han are 